---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privat Surabaya â€“ Pusat Les Privat Profesional" description="Solusi belajar privat terbaik di Surabaya dengan guru terverifikasi. Fleksibel, personal, dan terpercaya untuk SD, SMP, SMA, dan Umum.">
    <Header />
    
    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28 hero-bg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                    <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
                        Pusat Les Privat Terpercaya di Surabaya
                    </span>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-secondary tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
                        Solusi Belajar <span class="text-primary">Menyenangkan</span> dan <span class="relative inline-block">Fleksibel <div class="absolute w-full h-3 bg-accent/30 bottom-1 left-0 -z-10 rounded-sm"></div></span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                        Kami hadir menjadi solusi belajar dengan metode les privat yang memiliki pendekatan personal. Tentukan waktu, tempat, dan materi belajar sesuai kebutuhanmu.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                        <a href="/program-belajar" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 bg-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-sky-600 transition shadow-lg shadow-sky-500/20">
                            Lihat Program
                            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/kontak" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-slate-700 border border-slate-200 font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition shadow-sm">
                            Hubungi Kami
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Decorative blobs -->
            <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-purple-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-30 animate-blob"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-20 right-10 w-72 h-72 bg-sky-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-30 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Section -->
        <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-blue-600 rounded-2xl opacity-20 blur-lg rotate-2"></div>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1471&q=80" alt="Students learning" class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover h-[400px]">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary mb-6">Kenapa Memilih Privat Surabaya?</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Fleksibilitas Waktu & Tempat</h3>
                                    <p class="text-slate-600">Belajar kapan saja dan di mana saja. Kamu yang tentukan jadwalnya.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Pendekatan Personal</h3>
                                    <p class="text-slate-600">Metode belajar disesuaikan dengan karakter dan kebutuhan setiap siswa.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path></svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Tutor Berkualitas</h3>
                                    <p class="text-slate-600">Pengajar terseleksi dari universitas ternama dan berpengalaman.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Location/Office Section -->
        <section class="py-20 bg-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="bg-secondary rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2">
                        <div class="p-10 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Kantor Kami</h2>
                            <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                                Kami menyediakan tempat belajar yang nyaman di kantor kami, didesain khusus untuk kegiatan les privat dan pelayanan lainnya di lokasi strategis.
                            </p>
                            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                                <div class="flex items-center text-slate-300">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-4 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                                    <span>Jl. Pemuda No. 12, Surabaya</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center text-slate-300">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-4 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>
                                    <span>(022) 1234 5678</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/4iPCqXqebAnbwwdp9" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-600 transition">
                                    Lihat di Google Maps
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-80 lg:h-auto bg-slate-700 relative">
                            <!-- Placeholder for map or office image -->
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1469&q=80" alt="Office Interior" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/50"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="py-20 bg-primary">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Siap Meraih Prestasi Impianmu?</h2>
                <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Bergabunglah dengan ribuan siswa lainnya yang telah sukses bersama Privat Surabaya. Konsultasikan kebutuhan belajarmu sekarang.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                    <a href="https://wa.me/6282366879000" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-50 transition shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"/></svg>
                        Chat WhatsApp
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <Footer />
</Layout>
